## Prioritization rubric

Score each dimension **1–3** (higher = sooner). Sum or use P0/P1/P2 labels.

| Dimension | 3 (high) | 1 (low) |
|-----------|----------|---------|
| **Impact** | Unblocks pilot KPI / daily ops | Nice-to-have polish |
| **Risk** | Wrong data / margin / FIFO if delayed | Reversible UI tweak |
| **Dependencies** | Others waiting on this | Blocked by open decision |

**P0:** pilot-critical (dashboard truth, finance aggregates, FIFO alerts, deploy path).  
**P1:** operational depth (CRM CRUD, checklist completion, finance input).  
**P2:** docs, reglements, design polish.

Tie-break: **fewer dependencies first**, then **Human Architect** call.

---

## Splitting epics (`T-0xx`)

| Rule | Example |
|------|---------|
| One **shippable slice** per task (≤ ~1–2 dev days) | T-010 «Guest detail read» separate from «Booking create» if large |
| **Vertical** slice preferred (UI + API + seed) | `/finance` entry for one `RevenueLine` type |
| **Horizontal** only for shared infra | T-002 schema before module UIs |
| Number **sequentially**; never reuse IDs | Next free: T-015 after T-014 |
| Epic name in «Детали» Notes, not in ID | Epic «Phase 3 CRM» → T-010, T-011… |

---

## `BACKLOG` vs `BLOCKED`

| Status | Use when |
|--------|----------|
| **BACKLOG** | Idea valid but AC/deps unclear; no Architect answer needed yet |
| **READY** | DoR met; assignee can start |
| **BLOCKED** | **Cannot proceed** without Architect decision (auth provider, tenant model, legal/pilot sign-off) |

**BLOCKED** must include in task Notes: **question**, **options**, **recommended default**, **who decides**.

---

## Coordination with other roles

| Role | PM hands off | PM expects back |
|------|----------------|-----------------|
| **Developer** | READY + AC + `@prisma` / module paths | PR summary in «Итог»; scope questions → PM `BLOCKED` |
| **UI/UX** | Layout/KPI ids in brief or `@design-tokens.md` | Tokens/wireframe before dev-heavy UI task READY |
| **QA** | Testable AC; link to `qa-checklist.md` | Pass/fail; PM does not override failed AC |
| **Human** | `BLOCKED` decisions, priority disputes | Written answer in chat → PM updates queue |

**Parallel agents:** different task IDs only; before merge reconcile **one** `orchestration-queue.md` source of truth.

