## Management & roadmap docs

| Doc | PM updates when |
|-----|-----------------|
| `knowledge-base/product-brief.md` | MVP scope, metrics, personas, module P0/P1 |
| `knowledge-base/architecture.md` | New module, entity, integration boundary |
| `docs/roadmap.md` | Phase completed or reprioritized |
| `docs/management-overview.md` | **Non-technical** narrative for owners (after feature ships or pilot reglement) |
| `docs/technical-overview.md` | Usually **Developer**; PM only if no dev available and Architect asks |

