## Banya-Digital: pilot metrics (lightweight)

When grooming **banya-digital**, align tasks with `@knowledge-base/product-brief.md` metrics:

| Metric | Target (v1 pilot) | Typical task hook |
|--------|-------------------|-------------------|
| Close shift time | −30% vs tables | T-013 checklists + ops UX |
| Inventory accuracy | ≥95% | T-012 FIFO UI + movements |
| Margin visibility | Daily per hall | T-011 finance input + dashboard |
| Kitchen↔SPA conflicts | 0 unprocessed/shift | T-011 operations timings |
| KPI from DB | 100% on dashboard | T-006+ regression in QA |

Optional competitor/pilot note in brief «Референсы» — not blocking unless Architect asks.

